      <title>南非失业率创两年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/south-africa-jobless-rate-at-two-year-high-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二季度失业率意外上升至2022年以来的最高水平，截至6月的三个月内达到33.5%，而上一季度为32.9%。南非统计局公布的数据显示，贸易和农业部门在此期间失业人数最多。彭博社的詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾在约翰内斯堡报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/south-africa-jobless-rate-at-two-year-high-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员充分预期英国央行今年将再降息两次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/traders-fully-price-two-more-boe-rate-cuts-this-year-after-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数据显示通胀增速低于预期后，交易员增加了对英国央行今年降息的押注，完全预期英国央行将再降息两次，每次降息25个基点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/traders-fully-price-two-more-boe-rate-cuts-this-year-after-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银首席执行官埃尔莫蒂谈盈利、市场波动和美联储利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/in-full-ubs-ceo-ermotti-on-earnings-volatility-fed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银首席执行官 Sergio Ermotti 讨论了第二季度收益、市场波动和美联储利率前景。在瑞银公布高于预期的利润并看到其关键财富管理业务客户流入强劲后，他在苏黎世与 Francine Lacqua 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-14/in-full-ubs-ceo-ermotti-on-earnings-volatility-fed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 06:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
